      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "\"Observe their customs, gentlemen; they are mere chaos masquerading as life, a savage existence devoid of the proper institutions that elevate man. Their tribal squabbles and superstitious rituals are nothing more than impediments to true human potential. Without the firm hand of European law and the steady guidance of our civilization, this region will remain a festering swamp of barbarism, perpetually stunted and incapable of achieving its proper station among nations. We do not conquer for sport; we intervene to elevate them from their brutish state to something worthy of the light.\"",
